description: Fineqia International Inc., through its subsidiaries, operates a regulated crowdfunding platform that focuses on debt instruments. It provides an online platform and associated services to support security issuances and manage the administration of debt securities. The company was formerly known as NanoStruck Technologies Inc. and changed its name to Fineqia International Inc. in August 2016. Fineqia International Inc. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
